```json
{
  "application": "LAMMPS",
  "details": {
    "resource_manager": "LSF",
    "scheduler_directives": [
      "BSUB -P MAT201",
      "BSUB -J 8PSU_H_2000MVm_-x",
      "BSUB -o std.oe%J",
      "BSUB -W 2:00",
      "BSUB -nnodes 1",
      "BSUB -alloc_flags \"gpumps smt1\""
    ],
    "environment_variables": [
      "ESPRESSO_PSEUDO",
      "LSB_INTERACTIVE",
      "LS_SUBCWD",
      "LSB_MAX_NUM_PROCESSORS"
    ],
    "libraries": "lammps",
    "runtime_parameters": {
      "Ncpu": "LSB_MAX_NUM_PROCESSORS - 1",
      "Nnode": "Ncpu / 42",
      "Ngpu": "Nnode * 6",
      "Nmpi": "Ngpu",
      "N_rs": "Nmpi",
      "N__r": "N_rs / Nnode",
      "N__a": "Nmpi / N_rs",
      "N__g": "Ngpu / N_rs",
      "N__c": "Ncpu / N_rs",
      "N_kt": "N__c / N__a",
      "N_kg": "N__g / N__a"
    },
    "execution_command": "jsrun -n${N_rs} -a${N__a} -c${N__c} -g${N__g} -r${N__r} --bind none --latency_priority cpu-memory --smpiargs \"-gpu\" ${my_lmp_mpi} -nocite -k on g ${N_kg} t ${N_kt} -sf kk -pk kokkos newton on -i ./nvt.lmpi"
  }
}
```
